  <h1>Delicious Pasta Recipe</h1>
  <p>This is a simple and tasty pasta recipe that you can make at home.</p>

  <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>250g pasta</li>
    <li>2 cups tomato sauce</li>
    <li>1 cup grated cheese</li>
    <li>1 tablespoon olive oil</li>
    <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions:</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Boil the pasta according to package instructions.</li>
    <li>Heat olive oil in a pan, add tomato sauce, salt, and pepper. Cook until heated through.</li>
    <li>Mix the cooked pasta with the sauce.</li>
    <li>Sprinkle grated cheese on top and serve!</li>
  </ol>

